      "dimensions": 1,
      "description": "extend -  - Sets the extend conditions to determine what happens to the blur at the edge of the image.\n\n hold - The blur is clamped at the edges. zero - The blue is calculated as if the image does not extend past its edges. repeat - The blur is calculated as if the image was repeating (tiled - blurring at the bottom of image that would fall outside the image edges will appear at top of image). mirror - The blur is calculated as if the image was mirrored and repeating.",
